      "body" : "@S.N. - You are misinterpreting.  That is the &gt;&gt;default&lt;&lt; value for the classpath.   If you supply an explicit classpath via <code>$CLASSPATH</code> or <code>-cp</code> or any other way, then the default classpath is not relevant.  The OP is using <code>-cp</code>."
