      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "I know you&#39;re supposed to avoid comments like &quot;ugh&quot;, but that&#39;s exactly how I feel about this.  I&#39;m using a colon in my classpath and the engine isn&#39;t complaining at all about an illegal classpath!  It just says &quot;Could not find or load main class&quot;.  I searched for that error when I realized I must be doing something stupid.  Thank you!"
