    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>You must ensure that you add the location of your <code>.class</code> file to your classpath. So, if its in the current folder, add <code>.</code> to your classpath.\nNote that the Windows classpath separator is a semi-colon, i.e. a <code>;</code>.</p>\n"
