    "question_id" : 7485670,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I was using Java 1.8, and this error suddenly occurred when I pressed \"Build and clean\" in NetBeans. I switched for a brief moment to 1.7 again, clicked OK, re-opened properties and switched back to 1.8, and everything worked perfectly.</p>\n\n<p>I hope I can help someone out with this, as these errors can be quite time-consuming.</p>\n"
