    "answer_id" : 24212404,
    "question_id" : 7485670,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>This solved the issue for me today:</p>\n\n<pre><code>cd /path/to/project\ncd build\nrm -r classes\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Then clean&amp;build it and run the individual files you need.</p>\n"
