    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I got this error because I was trying to run</p>\n\n<pre><code>javac HelloWorld.java &amp;&amp; java HelloWorld.class\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>when I should have removed <code>.class</code>:</p>\n\n<pre><code>javac HelloWorld.java &amp;&amp; java HelloWorld\n</code></pre>\n"
